Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:52.42,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sanji parted ways with the Straw Hats\Nafter the duel against Luffy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:54.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He thought he was determined but
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he found himself leaving \Nthe Whole Cake Chateau.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Afterwards, Luffy and Sanji saw each \Nother again at the rendezvous point.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you {\i1}really{\i0} want!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go back to the Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't get the courage to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the wedding begins, I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can't stop anything by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.30,0:03:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even consider...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...those scum as my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna save their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's how you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got us! Let's crash the wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Sanji Comes Back!\NCrash! The Tea Party from Hell!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:30.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,OUTSKIRTS OF SWEET CITY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei came to help?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good. So Nami-{\i1}san{\i0} is okay too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, the problem is\Nhow we join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once they hear you're coming back,\NI'm sure they'll be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry - we should never have done this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too ashamed to see Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami and the others care about you\Nmore than I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I scared her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the rain is stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:51.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,MIRRO-WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?! Chobro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think they can hear us\Nthrough this piece of glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mirror I was talking \Nthrough the last time we spoke
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,broke on the tree monster Kingbaum's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I think there is at least a piece of glass\Nthat connects to this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you there, Luffy?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is that...?\N--It's Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Answer me if you're there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy! Can you hear me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! It's a piece of glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you hear me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is his voice coming from a mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a long story but\Nthey're in a mirror dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mirror dimension? Chopper and the others?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, Luffy! Great! You're really there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Is Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0} there too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!\NSo you got to see him again, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0}, I'm glad that you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:08:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saved everybody from \Ninside the mirror, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook even got a copy of the Ponegliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm impressed with you guys!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your compliment doesn't make me happy,\Nyou fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You silly little goose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, it's good that Sanji's there\Nbut did you guys come to an agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji is not coming back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna crash Big Mom's tea party\Nand the wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and save Sanji's family!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Sanji'll be back with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B... Big...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! She's the Emperor of the Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want risk everyone's...\NI mean, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}'s life over a personal issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:10:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you and Luffy got into a big fight\Nso I was worried, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so relieved! Really, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You simpleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we do that, then Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0} will \Ncome back to us, right, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For terrifying me like that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But let's forget about it for now.\NThere isn't much time left before the tea party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna get you back no matter what,\NSanji-kun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Is it a proposal, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:08.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THUMP
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why but I feel as ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Luffy, we know what to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Sanji's sister saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I wanna save them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, let's save them all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it won't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're not aiming to\Ntake Big Mom down,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she always looks forward to\Nthose tea parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By crashing it,\Nwe'll unleash the Emperor's wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:12:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, I think you guys have already faced\Nvarious Ministers on the island,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they are just the tip of the iceberg\Nof the Big Mom Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even tougher ones will attend the tea party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And underground rulers\Nfrom around the world are invited too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other side, there are only...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ten of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't count us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fudge it!\NThere are only eight of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you all get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already told everyone down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I need to share something\Nthat sounds slightly unrelated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Capone "Gang" Bege, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Minister has arrived! Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:19.52,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THIRD SON OF CHARLOTTE\N (MINISTER OF BEANS)\NBIG MOM PIRATES
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:24.57,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,CHARLOTTE DAIFUKU
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait for Mama's tea party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:57.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,BIG MOM'S TEA PARTY STARTS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big Mom's tea party starts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:15:00.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,IN FIVE HOURS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...in five hours.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Capone "Gang" Bege, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's the one who took Sanji away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of the Worst Generation\Nwith a name as infamous as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the West Blue where he comes from,\Nfive powerful mafia families...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...rule their underground society.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Five Families of the West -\None of the bosses of the five...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was "Gang" Bege.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His nickname "Gang" traces \Nback to his younger days
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\when he became notorious as a hit-man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hit-man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he was a sick young man\Nwho liked to hurt helpless living things
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and watch them get weaker and weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How terrible is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did the same to crime families.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish it were more bitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lead tastes bitter, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when he became a young mobster,\Nhe always aimed to kill bosses of the underworld
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even after he got his own family,\Nhe only killed his rival bosses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:16:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you betraying me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're outnumbered!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Bege...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...never showed interest in \Nhis enemy's post or territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just took money and goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BLOODY TRAGEDY! AN INTERNAL FEUD?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WAKING NIGHTMARE! UNDERGROUND REMAINS TENSE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THE UNDERGROUND SOCIETY IN CHAOS\NTRIGGERED BY THE ASSASSINATION?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards he enjoyed watching\Nbloody tugs-of-war within groups
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and how it upset the leaders\Nthat were secretly connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is really a disgusting man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know he had such history.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a terrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you hit someone,\Nyou'll get hit back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:18:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He began to be targeted constantly\Nby those seeking vengeance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege even enjoyed that.\NHe built an impregnable castle and fought back,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then mocked his enemy's disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An impregnable castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess he still hasn't \Nshown all of his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After he got bored with life on land\Nand sailed out to sea, he did the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did this?! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He became infamous for targeting only the captains of\Nwell-known pirate groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone still targeted on the sea\Nby enemies seeking revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,being under the wing of the Emperor of the Sea\Nis the perfect safe haven.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he decided to affiliate with Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.43,0:19:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate how you work every day\Nso for the next tea party,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to put you in charge of security.\NDon't let me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom thought highly of his finely \Nhoned alertness and defensive capability.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he took the title of a "Rook" soldier\Nfor the upcoming tea party
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and has been entrusted with\Nfull authority over its security.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you telling us this now, Jimbei?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If security guards are on our side,\Nnothing can stand in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The main event of the tea \Nparty is the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you already know, Big Mom intends to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:20:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kill all the members of the \NVinsmokes at the wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and acquire all of Germa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege is going to kill Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?\NSeems like everyone has their own plot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, Pekoms who guided you guys to this island\Nwas actually taken by Bege and his clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and was approached to \Ncooperate with their plan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pekoms... So that's what happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You underestimate Mama too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.16,0:20:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Pekoms is a very loyal man,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.75,0:20:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bege let him fall into shark-filled \Nwaters to keep him quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my friends saw that\Nand saved him in the nick of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is now resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. So he's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Bege, I'll make him pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, here comes my main point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I came up with a plan\Nafter I learned everything from Pekoms.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I asked myself "What would you guys do?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was sure when you \Nlearned the whole thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you would say you want to \Nsave Sanji and his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for Pekoms\Nbut under the circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:22:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}do you really want to\Nmake an enemy of Bege?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The tea party starts at 10 in the morning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About five hours from now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike the ten of us\Nwho don't even have a plan yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't count us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.15,0:22:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn brutes!\NI'll let them know what you are up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.79,0:22:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen, Luffy,\NBege's group is fully prepared for today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.51,0:22:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's join Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.03,0:22:46.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A FEW HOURS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A few hours later,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.53,0:22:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Monkey D. Luffy, one of the Worst Generation,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:22:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and Capone "Gang" Bege.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:09.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Between these two pirates,\Nan unprecedented operation is hatched.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.57,0:23:26.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Changing into a new outfit,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.79,0:23:30.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the others prepare\Nfor the impending tea party!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:33.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The two rogues from the East and the West!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:36.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Bege are incompatible \Nwith each other!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.29,0:23:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In a tense atmosphere,\Na forbidden meeting now begins!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.49,0:23:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Secret Meeting! Luffy \Nvs. the Fire Tank Pirates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.71,0:23:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.97,0:23:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.97,0:23:52.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
